t whenever it is spotted.  I'll try to keep your date in mind when Dreadstorm is killing stuff though, and try to give it a good chance of showing up for the 7th.<br>2) You're going to need a few key classes at a fairly high level (especially shaman/chanter, to slow).  It'd be a good idea to ask around and try to get a few 58+ who'd be willing to help.<br>3) You're going to spend a lot of time working out the pull and CRing pullers if you've never done it before, don't get discourraged.  Stick with it, and try some more creative techniques if you don't get it the first time <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>4) He almost always drops 1 or 2 Shadeork belts, and seems to drop 2 pieces + 1 spell max.  Sometimes no spell..  in any case, don't be disappointed if the loot isn't great; it'd be a great accomplishment for an open raid!<br><br>Again, good luck Nueelien..  if you get really stumped, bug me and I might try to help out <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br> <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=137021">Baron Saurix Shizathir</a><br>Myrmidon of Cabilis, 59th Rank</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.showNextMessage?topicID=125.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=125.topic&index=8><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.threadControl?topicID=125.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professio